author: craigmcc
msg: First round of Javadoc whining cleanups -- 32 more to go.  No functionality
changes.
JDK 1.4 is much pickier about this kind of thing.

author: craigmcc
msg: With Ted's permission, remodel the build.xml file to conform to
the conventions of non-Mavenized commons projects.  Explicitly
declare dependencies (with replaceable parameters) in "build.xml"
with sample definitions in "build.properties.sample".  Add a
manifest file to the generated JAR file.  Fix a mis-named package
declaration in CommandStore.
There are still a bunch of warnings from Javadoc, but those can be
dealt with separately.

author: husted
msg: + PropertiesException: Generalize message.
+ StorageBeanBase: Add support for reading command parameters from
a *.param line for each query.
+ StorageBean*: Add paramList property (to ease migration to Commons.SQL)
+ StorageBean*,ProcessBean*: Move Remote* properties to ProcessBean.
+ ResultSetUtils: Deprecate setProperties in favor of BeanUtils.copyProperties.
+ ConvertUtils: Add tokenTo* methods.
+ build.xml: Add option for compling with debugging code.
+ StorageBeanBase: isNew: change to use String or Number validation
when value is not null; store: Fix to use isNew.
